                    Once you delete your account, there is no going back. All
                    your data including articles, listings, and awards will be
                    permanently removed.
                </p>
                <button
                    type="button"
                    class="px-6 py-3 border-2 border-red-200 text-red-500 rounded-xl font-bold uppercase text-sm tracking-wide hover:bg-red-500 hover:text-white hover:border-red-500 transition-all"
